hpnicfe1Table.name: hpnicfe1Table
hpnicfe1Table.description: A list of E1 interface entries.

hpnicfe1Entry.name: hpnicfe1Entry
hpnicfe1Entry.description: This entry contains E1 interface management information.

HpnicfE1TimeSlot.name: HpnicfE1TimeSlot
HpnicfE1TimeSlot.description: Each octet within this value specifies a set of time slots, with the first octet specifying time slot 1 through 8, the second octet specifying time slots 9 through 16, etc. Within each octet, the most significant bit represents the highest numbered time slot, and the least significant bit represents the lowest numbered time slot. Thus, each time slot of the E1 is represented by a single bit within the value of this object. If that bit has a value of '1' then that time slot is included in the set of time slots; the time slot is not included if its bit has a value of '0'.

hpnicfe1Type.name: hpnicfe1Type
hpnicfe1Type.description: Specifies the type of the E1 interface. Now it supports types as follow: voice voice type pos POS type

hpnicfe1Clock.name: hpnicfe1Clock
hpnicfe1Clock.description: Specifies the clock type used on the E1 interface.

hpnicfe1FrameFormat.name: hpnicfe1FrameFormat
hpnicfe1FrameFormat.description: Specifies the frame format used on the E1 interface.

hpnicfe1LineCode.name: hpnicfe1LineCode
hpnicfe1LineCode.description: Specifies the line code type used on the E1 interface.

hpnicfe1PriSetTimeSlot.name: hpnicfe1PriSetTimeSlot
hpnicfe1PriSetTimeSlot.description: This is a bit-map of PRI time slots used on the E1 interface. It needs to administratively shut down the D channel of the E1 interface before cancelling PRI time slots.

hpnicfe1DChannelIndex.name: hpnicfe1DChannelIndex

hpnicfe1SubScribLineChannelIndex.name: hpnicfe1SubScribLineChannelIndex

hpnicfe1FcmChannelIndex.name: hpnicfe1FcmChannelIndex

hpnicfe1InterfaceTable.description: A list of channels of E1 interface entries. Including D channels and subscriber-line channels.

hpnicfe1InterfaceEntry.name: hpnicfe1InterfaceEntry
